generated_description: expo marcos is a company based in guadalajara, jalisco that specializes in framing services. they offer a wide variety of frames in classic, modern, contemporary, and vintage finishes, as well as paintings, oil paintings, lithographs, and mirrors. their main focus is on preserving and enhancing the elegance of any space, whether it be for a home or office. they also offer custom-made mirrors with or without beveled edges. customers can bring in their own ideas or images for printing on photographic paper or canvas. expo marcos has multiple locations, including expo marcos wal-mart, expo marros real center, expo marcos plaza san miguel, and expo marmos universidad.
